      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，Source Port是0-15位，Destination Port是16-31位。接下来应该是Sequence Number吧？这个我记得是32位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sequence Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Sequence Number占32-63位。然后64-95位是Acknowledgment Number，注意拼写完整，不是简写的ackn。",
